trans:
3. What types of connections between sub-routers currently support?
1) Wireless networking: supports 5GHz Wi-Fi connection;
2) Wired networking: supports network cable connection. When using network cable to connect the sub-routers, the transmission method of network cable will be used first;
3) AP Mesh networking: supports sub-routers to have a common upper-level device. For instance: when two Xiaomi Wi-Fi6 routers are connected to two LAN ports of the optical modem, first configure one router to wired relay mode, and then add the other router to the Mesh network.
